# Dataset Getting Started
created: undefined, last updated: 2026-05-06, [Read more](https://langfuse.com/docs/datasets/get-started)

Individual items can be added to a dataset by providing the input and optionally the expected output.
```
langfuse.create_dataset_item(
dataset_name="<dataset_name>",
# any python object or value, optional
input={
"text": "hello world"
},
# any python object or value, optional
expected_output={
"text": "hello world"
},
# metadata, optional
metadata={
"model": "llama3",
}
```
...
langfuse.createDatasetItem({
datasetName: "<dataset_name>",
// any JS object or value
input: {
text: "hello world",
},
// any JS object or value, optional
expectedOutput: {
text: "hello world",
},
// metadata, optional
metadata: {
model: "llama3",
},
});
...
langfuse.create_dataset_item(
dataset_name="<dataset_name>",
input={ "text": "hello world" },
expected_output={ "text": "hello world" },
# link to a trace
source_trace_id="<trace_id>",
# optional: link to a specific span, event, or generation
source_observation_id="<observation_id>"
